title: Manga Studio 5 (Clip Studio Paint) Brushes by Brian Allen
description:
I created this set of over 100 custom brushes for Manga Studio 5 (Clip Studio Paint) available for download for only $2.99.

This video quickly walks you through each set of brushes and shows them in use.

Included in the pack are

14 Inking Brushes
18 Paint Brushes
12 Pencil Brushes
5 Shading Brushes
16 Splatter Brushes
20+ Special Pattern Brushes
22 Texture BrushesThe brushes are useful for all styles of illustration. As a freelance digital illustrator, I use them primarily for Comic Book illustration, t-shirt design, logo design, character and concept illustration, sketching, and painting.
